divs: Sighting DetailsWhile taking photos of cloud formations I saw nothing in the sky. Upon viewing the photos on the computer this formation of three objects appeared in the picture. I never at any time realized there were any unknown objects in the sky. This particular picture had no clouds as I was taking random photographs at the time. I have a friend who has Adobe photoshop and she edited the file to enlarge and bring clarity to the photograph. Copy of original and edited file included. My wife was never a believer in UFO's but she is now.My first impression upon seeing the photograph is 'finally'. I have not seen one since 1968 in Vietnam.
Summary: Taking photos with my digital camera.
